    {
      "num": 2,
      "title": "こんな患者、外来にいませんか？",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起：HbA1c 7%台・痩せ型・経口薬でなんとか管理。実はSPIDDMかも。",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:30px}.alert-box{border-left:6px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:30px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-bottom:24px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:24px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 2 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>こんな患者、外来にいませんか？</h2><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>HbA1c 7%台、痩せ型（BMI 22以下）<br>メトホルミン＋DPP-4阻害薬で管理中<br>家族歴は乏しい<br>最近、徐々にコントロールが悪化してきた</p></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>その患者さんの抗GAD抗体、測定しましたか？<br>2型糖尿病の5〜10%が実はSPIDDM（緩徐進行1型）です</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 3,
      "title": "SPIDDMとは？ ── 診断基準2023",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承：SPIDDMの定義、診断マーカー、definiteとprobableの分類",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#134e4a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.card{background:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:16px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}.card-title{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#14b8a6;margin-bottom:10px}.card p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.two-col{display:flex;gap:20px}.two-col .card{flex:1}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 3 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>SPIDDMとは？ ── 診断基準（2023年改訂）</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">診断マーカー（膵島関連自己抗体）</div><p>抗GAD抗体（感度80%超） / 抗IA-2抗体 / 抗ZnT8抗体 / IAA<br>※2023年改訂で抗IA-2、IAA、ZnT8が新たに追加</p></div><div class=\"two-col\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">Definite（確定）</div><p>自己抗体陽性<br>＋インスリン依存状態<br>（内因性分泌が枯渇）</p></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">Probable（疑い）</div><p>自己抗体陽性<br>＋インスリン非依存<br>（まだ経口薬で管理可能）</p></div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 4,
      "title": "Tokyo Studyの衝撃的データ",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "承：SU薬群43% vs インスリン群10%のインスリン依存進行率",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:30px}.compare{display:flex;gap:30px;margin-bottom:24px}.compare-card{flex:1;border-radius:16px;padding:30px;text-align:center}.compare-bad{background:rgba(239,68,68,0.15);border:2px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.4)}.compare-good{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.4)}.compare-label{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#94a3b8}.compare-num{font-size:64px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:8px}.compare-bad .compare-num{color:#f87171}.compare-good .compare-num{color:#2dd4bf}.compare-desc{font-size:24px;color:#e2e8f0}.note{font-size:24px;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;line-height:1.6}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 4 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Tokyo Study ── SU薬 vs 早期インスリン</h2><div class=\"compare\"><div class=\"compare-card compare-bad\"><div class=\"compare-label\">SU薬群</div><div class=\"compare-num\">43%</div><div class=\"compare-desc\">がインスリン依存に進行<br>5年で分泌能が明らかに低下</div></div><div class=\"compare-card compare-good\"><div class=\"compare-label\">早期インスリン群</div><div class=\"compare-num\">10%</div><div class=\"compare-desc\">のみがインスリン依存に<br>分泌能が比較的保たれた</div></div></div><div class=\"note\">Maruyama T, et al. Ann N Y Acad Sci 2003;1005:362-369</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 5,
      "title": "DPP-4阻害薬の問題点",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "転：β細胞刺激作用があり、疾患修飾効果はない",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#134e4a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.card{background:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 32px;margin-bottom:16px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.06);padding:24px 32px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-bottom:16px}.card p,.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#334155}.point-box p{color:#991b1b;font-weight:700}.card-title{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#14b8a6;margin-bottom:8px}.source{font-size:18px;color:#64748b;margin-top:8px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 5 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>DPP-4阻害薬 ── SPIDDMでの問題点</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">作用機序</div><p>GLP-1/GIP分解を抑制 → β細胞のインスリン分泌を促進<br>血糖依存性だが、自己免疫で傷ついたβ細胞への負荷は残る</p></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>β細胞機能の改善は薬剤使用中のみ。疾患修飾効果（β細胞の保護・再生）は認められていない（最大2年の観察）</p></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">メタアナリシスの結論</div><p>1型糖尿病でDPP-4阻害薬を併用してもHbA1cの有意な低下なし</p><div class=\"source\">Guo H, et al. J Diabetes Res 2018</div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 6,
      "title": "Take Home Message",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:16px;padding:28px 36px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;color:#0d4a4a;background:#fff;width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 6 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Take Home Message</h2><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">1</span><span class=\"thm-text\">痩せ型・コントロール不良の糖尿病には<br>抗GAD抗体を必ず測定する</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">2</span><span class=\"thm-text\">SPIDDM疑いではSU薬を即中止<br>DPP-4阻害薬も漫然と継続しない</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">3</span><span class=\"thm-text\">Cペプチドを定期フォローし<br>低下傾向で早期インスリン導入</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
